text: Kenan & Kel is an American sitcom created by Kim Bass. The show was one of the spin-offs from All That. It aired on the Nickelodeon from 15 July, 1996 to 15 July, 2000 for four seasons and 65 episodes. It was show in Chicago and starring Kenan Thompson, Kel Mitchell, Ken Foree, Vanessa Baden, Teal Marchande and Dan Frischman. ==Other websites== * Category:Comedy television series Category:Nickelodeon television series Category:1996 American television series debuts Category:2000 American television series endings Category:Television spin-offs Category:English-language television programs
